liblangtag
=============

An interface library to access tags for identifying languages

Features
===========
- several subtag registry database supports:
  - language
  - extlang
  - script
  - region
  - variant
  - extension
  - grandfathered
  - redundant
- handling of the language tags
  - parser
  - matching
  - canonicalizing

Requirements
===============

- libxml2
- GObject Introspection (if you like)

